{"tid":1544038,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"警察打人 - 邁克","createTime":"2019-09-05T11:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T12:07:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3cba19206c3646abecc705acd8b91a826ba62c4","tid":1544038,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T11:57:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20190905/20762127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762127&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWA2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=c97e660e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2582%2581%25E5%2585%258B%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190905%2F20762127&h=652f96cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%82%81%E5%85%8B/daily/article/20190905/20762127</a><br />\n<br />\n警察打人 - 邁克<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190905/large/1567579697_82f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190905%2Flarge%2F1567579697_82f9.jpg&h=90c08a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港警察幾時變得如此脆弱，路人語重心長垂詢「良心去咗邊」，居然即場被打到頭破血流，事後記者仗義追問，慣性耍嘴皮子的發言人還支支吾吾，顧左右而偏偏不言他？恕我政治極端不正確，這樣刁蠻的反應真係乸型到不能，從前粵語片只得鳳凰女小姐偶爾會表演，男人大丈夫就算有鋪易服癮，也不敢貿貿然鵲巢鳩佔。堂堂紀律部隊遭質疑個心畀狗食咗，點會蠢到立刻以行動證實傳聞並非空穴來風，連最基本的操守也沒有，怪不得習總訪港彈出一句「這是正式錄用的警察嗎」，可見他老人家幾犀利，龍眼輕輕一掃妖怪原形畢露。這可不是個別例子，前幾天區議員李世鴻在大圍站就因為講了「黑警暴打市民可恥」，耳尖的洋警司便吩咐爪牙將他推倒在地，使蠻力拘捕帶返差館，該名受薪保護市民的公僕還有個漂亮中文名字哩，可惜行為舉止與「潘毅德」格格不入，完全浪費了師爺一番心機。<br />\n<br />\n和我一樣政治不正確的張愛玲，有一天在一九四幾年的外灘見到警察無緣無故打人，「大約因為我的思想沒受過訓練之故，這時候我並不想起階級革命，一氣之下，只想去做官，或是做主席夫人，可以走上前給那警察兩個耳刮子」。自稱向來很少有正義感的她，「不願意看見什麼，就有本事看不見，然而這一回，我忍不住屢屢回過頭去望，氣塞胸膛，打一下，就覺得我的心收縮一下」，跟住「惡狠狠盯住他看，恨不得眼睛裏飛出小刀子，很希望我能夠表達出充份的鄙夷與憤怒」。嘩，好險呀，換了今時今日香港，市民怒睥警察，是會隨時被控阻差辦公及暴動的！ <br />\n<br />\n邁克<br />\n電郵 :heartsociety2@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n滿手鮮血，行街恤髮 (李碧華)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n極權下的正常 (曾志豪)"},{"pid":"5a65a2b65c4823599dcf7c4a449457ac9c96067c","tid":1544038,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:04:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。